extends layout

block content
  section.page-hero
    p.eyebrow Our story
    h1 About Us
    p Family-owned, downtown-loved, and serving fresh donuts since 1992.

  section.about-section
    div.about-card
      h2.logo-script Downtown Donuts
      p Downtown Donuts started as a small family-owned shop in 1992. Since then, it has become a cozy downtown stop for fresh donuts, warm coffee, and friendly faces.
      p This prototype uses a minimal and modern layout while keeping the brand warm and welcoming. The goal is to make the website easy for customers to use, especially on mobile devices.

    div.timeline-card
      h2 Sweet History
      div.timeline-item
        span 1992
        p Downtown Donuts opens as a small family-owned donut and coffee shop.
      div.timeline-item
        span Today
        p The shop continues serving the downtown community with classic donuts, coffee, and a cozy atmosphere.
      div.timeline-item
        span Next
        p A new website helps customers view the menu, order online, and leave comments.

  section.section
    div.section-heading
      p.eyebrow What matters
      h2 Simple, warm, and easy to use.
    div.feature-grid
      article.feature-card
        h3 Mobile Friendly
        p The layout is built to look clean on phones, tablets, and desktops.
      article.feature-card
        h3 Brand Focused
        p The design uses Downtown Donuts colors, typography, and cozy style.
      article.feature-card
        h3 Customer Connected
        p Customers can find ordering links and leave comments on the site.